// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2216 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 24a1e058-6432-5e48-9234-dd6acdb7a1df

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
